items.title: Bills Keeping Foreign Money Out Of Ballot Measure Campaigns Pick Up Steam In Republican States
items.description: Republican lawmakers in several states are making a concerted effort to keep foreign money out of ballot initiative campaigns.

items.title: Chat Logs Show Queer NSA Employees Discussing Perverted Acts At Work
